{"tid":1981120,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"一名武漢肺炎患者康復出院後 測試再驗出陽性反應","createTime":"2020-04-20T13:05:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-20T13:14:06.000Z","uid":21470,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d6f1006ec76711e16cffeedb5e57cccde0f36280","tid":1981120,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T13:05:53.000Z","msg":"新冠肺炎康復出院後 測試再驗出陽性反應<br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】據了解 ，一名新冠肺炎患者康復出院後，病毒測試再有初步陽性反應。<br />\n<br />\n病人是17歲英國留學生，上月22日返港，於香港仔金豐大廈接受家居檢疫，期間咳嗽及喉嚨痛，上月27日確診，本月初康復出院。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，他再出現輕微病徵，到瑪麗醫院急症室求醫，對新型冠狀病毒測試初步結果呈陽性，目前在瑪麗醫院留醫。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=388364\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D388364&d=1E6MrqGGcFSEGQF%2FdL0KzQp4YzggAwntK9UjHSQ2u7w%3D&h=bc263f44\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D388364&h=9d3d13c0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=388364</a>"},{"pid":"62d1408669fe0128a937c7d49bb2a7fceb33634b","tid":1981120,"uid":219429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T13:09:24.000Z","msg":"好撚慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"884a725029731ba255113dab6689a18e3f5308e1","tid":1981120,"uid":180302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T13:10:44.000Z","msg":"會唔會變左做永不完的疫症"},{"pid":"8fda593aeb12905e3f703a910c88f8ee17cf9bec","tid":1981120,"uid":106672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"62d1408669fe0128a937c7d49bb2a7fceb33634b","tid":1981120,"uid":219429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T13:09:24.000Z","msg":"好撚慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T13:12:10.000Z","msg":"有乜野慘過中招，就係中兩次<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" cla